DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ eBox components

	+ ebox

+ Debian packages (apt-get install <package>)
	
	+ libapt-pkg-perl

INSTALLATION
------------

- Once EBox base has been installed:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect EBox base path to install

- You should configure debconf and ucf not to ask questions when
  installing/upgrading a package.
